                <note rend="inline" type="source">817.48 Earthquake of 1931/15: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        President of Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Moncada</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-03-31">March 31,
                            1931</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I am profoundly distressed by the reports of the overwhelming disaster which has
                    befallen Nicaragua. Please be assured of my heartfelt sympathy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Henry L. Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
